<text><body>
<lb ed="W" n="0414a08"/><milestone unit="juan" n="1"/><mulu type="卷" n="1"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0414a09"/><div1 type="other"><mulu type="其他" level="1" label="錄文二"/><head>〔錄文二〕</head>
<lb ed="W" n="0414a10"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0414a11"/><p id="pW03p0414a1101" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em"><note place="inline">首殘</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0414a12"/><p id="pW03p0414a1201" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">如合拳。其上平偃，猶<note n="0414002" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「猶」，底本作「由」，據北245號改。</note>如<note n="0414003" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「如」，底本無，據北245號補。</note>天蓋。三念<note n="0414004" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「三念」，底本殘缺，據文意補。</note>佛。</p>
<lb ed="W" n="0414a13"/><p id="pW03p0414a1301" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛頭上有八萬<note n="0414005" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「萬」，底本作「方」，據文意改。</note>四千髮，一一髮長<note n="0414006" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「一一發長」，底本作「一一發長，一一發長」，據文意刪。</note>一丈三尺五
<lb ed="W" n="0414a14"/>寸，猶如黑絲<note n="0414007" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「五寸，猶如黑絲」，底本殘缺，據北245號補。</note>分齊分明，四觚分明，毛皆兩靡，右旋而
<lb ed="W" n="0414a15"/>生，如紺琉璃色。右旋<note n="0414008" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「旋」，底本無，據北245號補。</note>婉轉，卷成螺文，在佛頭上，一
<lb ed="W" n="0414a16"/>一毛孔，旋生五光，入諸光中。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0414a17"/><p id="pW03p0414a1701" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛頭皮黃金色，亦生眾光，入腦光十四色中。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0414a18"/><p id="pW03p0414a1801" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛頭頂骨其色正白如頗梨，雪山不得為譬。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0414a19"/><p id="pW03p0414a1901" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛腦紅頗梨色，有十四脈，眾畫具足，一一畫有十四
<lb ed="W" n="0414a20"/>光，分明了了，於腦脈中，旋生諸光，上衝頭骨，乃至髮際，
<pb ed="W" id="W03.0031b.0415a" n="0415a"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0415a01"/>光有十四色，圍繞眾髮。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0415a02"/><p id="pW03p0415a0201" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛髮際如赤真珠色，婉轉下垂，有五千光，間錯分明，
<lb ed="W" n="0415a03"/>皆向上靡，圍繞諸髮，從頂上出生諸化佛。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0415a04"/><p id="pW03p0415a0401" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">如來額廣平正，額上諸毛，毛皆上靡。其毛根下，梵
<lb ed="W" n="0415a05"/>摩尼色，毛端流光，如融紫金光相。上靡入於髮際。婉轉
<lb ed="W" n="0415a06"/>下垂至耳輪邊，然後布散入諸髮間，圍繞螺文數百千匝，
<lb ed="W" n="0415a07"/>從枕骨出如金蓮，華日照開，敷釋眾生意。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0415a08"/><p id="pW03p0415a0801" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛白毫相，長一丈六尺，十楞分明，如白琉璃筒，中外
<lb ed="W" n="0415a09"/>俱空，右旋婉轉，在佛眉間，圍如三寸，如白頗梨珠，十方
<lb ed="W" n="0415a10"/>光現，影閉眾目，如萬億日不可具見。於其毛端，出五色
<lb ed="W" n="0415a11"/>光明，還入毛孔。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0415a12"/><p id="pW03p0415a1201" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">如來左右二眉，形如初月，繞生諸毛，稠稀<note n="0415001" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「稠稀」，甲本作「稀稠」。</note>得所，
<lb ed="W" n="0415a13"/>眉光兩靡，散入諸髮，其色艷紫紺<note n="0415002" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「紫紺」，甲本作「紫艷紫紺」。</note>青琉璃豐翠，孔雀色
<lb ed="W" n="0415a14"/>無異類，猶<note n="0415003" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「猶」，甲本作「由」。</note>如聚墨，比琉璃光，眉下三畫及眼眶中旋生
<lb ed="W" n="0415a15"/>四光：青、黃、赤、白，上<note n="0415004" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「上」，甲本作「皆上」。</note>向艷出，入眉骨中，出眉毛端。
<lb ed="W" n="0415a16"/><note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0415a17"/><p id="pW03p0415a1701" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">如來眼睫上下各生<note n="0415005" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「生」，底本無，據甲本補。</note>五百毛，柔軟可愛，如優曇華
<lb ed="W" n="0415a18"/>鬚。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0415a19"/><p id="pW03p0415a1901" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛眼青白分明，白者白於白寶，青者勝青蓮華，上下
<lb ed="W" n="0415a20"/>俱瞬，如牛王目，目雙齊頭，旋出二光，如青蓮華。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0415a21"/><p id="pW03p0415a2101" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛耳普垂埵相，兩耳孔中，旋生七毛。輪郭眾相<note n="0415006" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「相」，底本無，據甲本補。</note>
<lb ed="W" n="0415a22"/>如寶蓮華，懸處日光，兩耳內外，出生蓮華及耳孔七毛，流
<pb ed="W" id="W03.0031b.0416a" n="0416a"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0416a01"/>出諸光，有五百支，支有五百色。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0416a02"/><p id="pW03p0416a0201" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">如來方頰車相，頰上六畫，中左右正等，有妙光色，輝
<lb ed="W" n="0416a03"/>艷倍常，如淨金色，譬如和合百千日月。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0416a04"/><p id="pW03p0416a0401" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">如來鼻高修直如鑄金鎚，當於面門，其孔流光，上下
<lb ed="W" n="0416a05"/>灌注。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0416a06"/><p id="pW03p0416a0601" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛髭鬚如科斗形，於毛端頭，開敷三光，紫紺紅色直
<lb ed="W" n="0416a07"/>從口邊旋頸上照，圍繞圓光作三種畫，其畫分明，色中上
<lb ed="W" n="0416a08"/>者。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0416a09"/><p id="pW03p0416a0901" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">如來師子欠<note n="0416001" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「欠」，甲本作「&CB11818;」。</note>相，佛張口時如師子王，口方正整等，
<lb ed="W" n="0416a10"/>口兩吻邊流出<note n="0416002" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「出」，底本無，據甲本補。</note>二光，其光金色。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0416a11"/><p id="pW03p0416a1101" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛唇色紅赤如頻婆果，於上下唇及齦&CB00171;間，和合出
<lb ed="W" n="0416a12"/>光<note n="0416003" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「光」，甲本無。</note>，其光團圓，猶<note n="0416004" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「猶」，甲本作「由」。</note>如百千赤真珠貫從佛口出，入於佛
<lb ed="W" n="0416a13"/>鼻，從佛鼻出，入白豪中，從白豪出，入諸髮間，影<note n="0416005" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「影」，甲本作「映」。</note>飾諸
<lb ed="W" n="0416a14"/>華。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0416a15"/><p id="pW03p0416a1501" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛口四十齒，齒印文上生光，其光紅白，光光相照，照
<lb ed="W" n="0416a16"/>四十齒，令四十齒聽然齊白如頗梨碧<note n="0416006" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「碧」，甲本作「碧色」。</note>，上下齊平，無參
<lb ed="W" n="0416a17"/>差者，其齒間之畫，流出諸光，亦紅白色，如是眾色，佛在
<lb ed="W" n="0416a18"/>世時，影<note n="0416007" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「影」，甲本作「映」。</note>曜人目。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0416a19"/><p id="pW03p0416a1901" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">如來上&CB00171;有<note n="0416008" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「有」，底本無，據甲本補。</note>八萬四千畫，了了分明，下齦如優曇
<lb ed="W" n="0416a20"/>&CB00425;華莖色。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<pb ed="W" id="W03.0031b.0417a" n="0417a"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0417a01"/><p id="pW03p0417a0101" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">如來廣長舌相，佛舌出時，如赤蓮華葉，<note n="0417001" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「葉」，底本無，據甲本補。</note>上至髮
<lb ed="W" n="0417a02"/>際，遍覆<note n="0417002" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「覆」，底本作「霞」，據甲本改。</note>佛面，其舌根下及舌兩邊有二寶珠流注甘露，
<lb ed="W" n="0417a03"/>滴舌<note n="0417003" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「舌」，底本作「射」，據文意改。</note>根上，諸天世人十地菩薩無此舌相，亦無此味，其
<lb ed="W" n="0417a04"/>舌上五畫五彩分明如寶印文。其舌下十脈眾光流出，如
<lb ed="W" n="0417a05"/>此上味入印文中，流注上下，入琉璃筒，諸佛笑時，動其舌
<lb ed="W" n="0417a06"/>跟此味力，故舌出五光，五色分明。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0417a07"/><p id="pW03p0417a0701" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛咽嗡相，光淨可愛如金翅鳥眼。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0417a08"/><p id="pW03p0417a0801" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛喉嚨如琉璃筒，狀若累蓮華，節節相重。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0417a09"/><p id="pW03p0417a0901" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛心如紅蓮華，金華影<note n="0417004" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「影」，甲本作「映」。</note>飾，妙琉璃筒懸在佛<note n="0417005" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「佛」，底本無，據甲本補。</note>胸，
<lb ed="W" n="0417a10"/>圍圜如心，開如不開，合如不合，紅華金光有八萬四千脈，
<lb ed="W" n="0417a11"/>猶<note n="0417006" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「猶」，甲本作「由」。</note>如天畫，一一畫中有八萬四千光，一一光明有八萬
<lb ed="W" n="0417a12"/>四千色，一一色中有無量微塵數化佛，一一化佛坐金剛
<lb ed="W" n="0417a13"/>臺，其金剛臺<note n="0417007" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「金剛臺」，甲本無。</note>放金色光，是諸化佛游佛心間，徑往五道
<lb ed="W" n="0417a14"/>度苦眾生。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0417a15"/><p id="pW03p0417a1501" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">如來頸臃圓相，三約分明，有二光<note n="0417008" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「二光」，甲本作「二種光」。</note>，其光萬色。<note place="inline">三念
<lb ed="W" n="0417a16"/>佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0417a17"/><p id="pW03p0417a1701" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛咽喉有三點相，分明猶<note n="0417009" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「猶」，甲本作「由」。</note>如伊字，一一點中流出
<lb ed="W" n="0417a18"/>二光。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0417a19"/><p id="pW03p0417a1901" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛缺盆骨，兩手兩足及項後七處<note n="0417010" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「處」，甲本作「寶」。</note>皆平滿相，光明
<pb ed="W" id="W03.0031b.0418a" n="0418a"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0418a01"/>遍照十方世界，作虎珀色。三念佛。</p>
<lb ed="W" n="0418a02"/><p id="pW03p0418a0201" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛兩肩膊圓滿相。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0418a03"/><p id="pW03p0418a0301" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">如來臂臃纖圓如象王鼻。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0418a04"/><p id="pW03p0418a0401" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛肘骨如龍王髮，婉轉相著節頭蟠龍不見其&CB00528;。<note place="inline">三念
<lb ed="W" n="0418a05"/>佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0418a06"/><p id="pW03p0418a0601" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛手十指纖長，參差不失其所，於一一指節端有十二
<lb ed="W" n="0418a07"/>輪相見<note n="0418001" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「見」，甲本作「現」。</note>。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0418a08"/><p id="pW03p0418a0801" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">如來赤銅爪，其爪八色，了了分明。佛手十指端各有
<lb ed="W" n="0418a09"/>萬字相，一一點間有千輻輪相。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0418a10"/><p id="pW03p0418a1001" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛手合縵掌，斂指不見，張時則見，如真珠網，分明可
<lb ed="W" n="0418a11"/>愛。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0418a12"/><p id="pW03p0418a1201" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛手掌文蘭成如自在天宮<note n="0418002" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「宮」，底本作「官」，據甲本改。</note>，其掌平正，人天無類，
<lb ed="W" n="0418a13"/>當於掌中，生千輻輪相，於十方面開摩尼光。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0418a14"/><p id="pW03p0418a1401" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛手背毛皆向上靡，如紺琉璃，流出五光，入網縵中。
<lb ed="W" n="0418a15"/><note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0418a16"/><p id="pW03p0418a1601" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛手足柔軟如天劫貝。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0418a17"/><p id="pW03p0418a1701" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛手內外握<note n="0418003" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「佛手內外握」，甲本無。</note>。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0418a18"/><p id="pW03p0418a1801" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛上身胸臆廣厚<note n="0418004" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「厚」，底本無，據北8299號補。</note>如師子王<note n="0418005" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「佛上身胸臆廣厚如師子王」，甲本無。</note>。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0418a19"/><p id="pW03p0418a1901" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛胸德字萬印相，中放三摩尼光。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0418a20"/><p id="pW03p0418a2001" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">如來腋下平滿，懸生五珠如摩尼<note n="0418006" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「尼」，甲本無。</note>珠，上柱於腋，有
<lb ed="W" n="0418a21"/>五百色光明，共相影發。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0418a22"/><p id="pW03p0418a2201" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛腹小不現相。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<pb ed="W" id="W03.0031b.0419a" n="0419a"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0419a01"/><p id="pW03p0419a0101" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛齊如毗楞伽寶珠，於其齊中有萬億寶華，一一寶華
<lb ed="W" n="0419a02"/>萬億那由他葉，一一葉萬億那由他色，一一色萬億那由他
<lb ed="W" n="0419a03"/>光。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0419a04"/><p id="pW03p0419a0401" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">如來脅肋大小正等，婉轉相著<note n="0419001" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「如來脅肋大小正等，婉轉相著」，甲本無。</note>。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0419a05"/><p id="pW03p0419a0501" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">如來諸骨枝節蟠龍相結，其間密緻<note n="0419002" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「如來諸骨枝節蟠龍相結，其間密緻」，甲本無。</note>。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0419a06"/><p id="pW03p0419a0601" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">如來鉤鎖骨卷舒自在不相妨礙，其骨色鮮白如頗梨，
<lb ed="W" n="0419a07"/>雪山不得為譬，上有紅光間錯成文，凝液<note n="0419003" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「液」，底本作「亦」，據北8299號改。</note>如脂<note n="0419004" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「脂」，底本作「之」，據北8299號改。</note>，皆
<lb ed="W" n="0419a08"/>出<note n="0419005" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「出」，甲本無。</note>金光。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0419a09"/><p id="pW03p0419a0901" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">如來馬王藏相，身根平滿，狀如滿月，有金色光，猶<note n="0419006" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「猶」，甲本作「由」。</note>
<lb ed="W" n="0419a10"/>如日輪。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0419a11"/><p id="pW03p0419a1101" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛兩&CB00170;周圓漸次而斂。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0419a12"/><p id="pW03p0419a1201" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛兩膝骨圓著好。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0419a13"/><p id="pW03p0419a1301" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">如來伊尼鹿王&CB00165;相。<app><lem wit="【CBETA】" resp="CBETA.maha"><note place="inline">三念佛</note>。</lem><rdg wit="【藏外】">三念佛</rdg></app></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0419a14"/><p id="pW03p0419a1401" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">如來足跟圓長有梵王頂相，眾類不異，各生一華，其
<lb ed="W" n="0419a15"/>華微妙，猶<note n="0419007" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「猶」，甲本作「由」。</note>如淨國優&CB00425;羅華。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0419a16"/><p id="pW03p0419a1601" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛兩足踝不見<note n="0419008" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「見」，甲本作「現」。</note>相。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0419a17"/><p id="pW03p0419a1701" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛足高平相<note n="0419009" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「佛足高平相」，甲本作「佛兩足膊高平相」，並置於「佛兩足踝不見相」前。</note>。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0419a18"/><p id="pW03p0419a1801" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛足膊上色如閻浮檀金色，毛皆上靡及身諸毛，隨一
<lb ed="W" n="0419a19"/>毛孔，一毛旋生，柔軟可愛。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<pb ed="W" id="W03.0031b.0420a" n="0420a"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0420a01"/><p id="pW03p0420a0101" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛足指網間如羅文彩，於其文間，眾色玄黃，不可具
<lb ed="W" n="0420a02"/>名。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0420a03"/><p id="pW03p0420a0301" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛足十指纖圓邪齊如<note n="0420001" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「如」，底本無，據甲本補。</note>赤銅爪，於其爪端有五師子
<lb ed="W" n="0420a04"/>口相。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0420a05"/><p id="pW03p0420a0501" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛腳十指端螺文相，如毗尼羯摩天所畫之印。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0420a06"/><p id="pW03p0420a0601" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">如來足下平滿不容一毛。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0420a07"/><p id="pW03p0420a0701" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛足下千輻輪相，轂輞具足，魚鱗相次，金剛<note n="0420002" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「剛」，底本作「則」，據甲本改。</note>處
<lb ed="W" n="0420a08"/>相。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0420a09"/><p id="pW03p0420a0901" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛那羅延力合以成身，結跏趺坐<note n="0420003" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「坐」，甲本作「坐坐」。</note>百寶蓮華座。<note place="inline">三
<lb ed="W" n="0420a10"/>念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0420a11"/><p id="pW03p0420a1101" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">若欲觀佛圓光者，世尊在日，若行之時，頂光照地。
<lb ed="W" n="0420a12"/>前一由旬純黃金色，後一由旬純黃金色，左一由旬純黃金
<lb ed="W" n="0420a13"/>色，右一由旬純黃金色。有人近佛左右行者，其人臭穢皆
<lb ed="W" n="0420a14"/>悉不現。人遠望之，同為金色。有人諦觀佛項光者，前行
<lb ed="W" n="0420a15"/>看者見佛在前，從後看者見佛在後，左邊看<note n="0420004" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「看」，底本無，據甲本補。</note>者見佛在
<lb ed="W" n="0420a16"/>左，右邊看者見佛在<note n="0420005" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「在」，底本作「左」，據文意改。</note>右。八方人來，遙見世尊項光<note n="0420006" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「項光」，底本無，據甲本補。</note>，
<lb ed="W" n="0420a17"/>各作是言：瞿曇沙門在金山中遊行，自在來向我所。如是
<lb ed="W" n="0420a18"/>眾生各各異見，此是項光相。<note place="inline">三念佛。</note></p>
<lb ed="W" n="0420a19"/><p id="pW03p0420a1901" rend="margin-left:0em;text-indent:2em">佛告阿難：如來有三十二大人相、八十種隨形好。金
<lb ed="W" n="0420a20"/>色光明，一一光明無量化佛，身諸毛孔一切變現及佛色
<pb ed="W" id="W03.0031b.0421a" n="0421a"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0421a01"/>身。略中說略<note n="0421001" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「略」，底本作「毗」，據甲本改。</note>者，我今為此時會大眾<note n="0421002" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「會大眾」，甲本作「大眾會」。</note>及淨飯王略說
<lb ed="W" n="0421a02"/>相好。佛生人間，示同人事。因人相故，說三十二相；勝
<lb ed="W" n="0421a03"/>諸天故，說八十種<note n="0421003" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「種」，底本無，據甲本補。</note>好；為諸菩薩，說<note n="0421004" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「說」，甲本無。</note>八萬四千諸妙相
<lb ed="W" n="0421a04"/>好、佛實<note n="0421005" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「實」，甲本作「寶」。</note>相好。我初成道摩伽陀國寂滅道場，為普賢
<lb ed="W" n="0421a05"/>賢首等諸大菩薩於雜華經已廣分別。此尊<note n="0421006" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「尊」，甲本作「等」。</note>法中所以
<lb ed="W" n="0421a06"/>略說，為諸凡夫及四部<note n="0421007" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「部」，底本無，據甲本補。</note>弟子謗方等經、作五逆罪、犯四
<lb ed="W" n="0421a07"/>重禁、偷僧祗物、婬比丘尼、破八戒齋，作諸惡事，種種耶
<lb ed="W" n="0421a08"/>見。如是等人若能<note n="0421008" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「能」，底本作「有能」，據甲本刪。</note>至心一日一夜繫念在前，觀佛如來
<lb ed="W" n="0421a09"/>一相好者，諸惡罪障皆悉滅盡。是故如來名婆伽婆、名阿
<lb ed="W" n="0421a10"/>羅訶、名三藐三佛陀<note n="0421009" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">「陀」，底本作「馱」，據文意改。</note>、名功德日、名智滿月、名清涼池、
<lb ed="W" n="0421a11"/>名除罪珠、名光明藏、名智慧山、名戒品河、名迷衢道、名
<lb ed="W" n="0421a12"/>邪見燈、名破煩惱賊、名一切眾生父母、名大歸依處。若
<lb ed="W" n="0421a13"/>有歸依佛世尊者，若稱名者，除百千劫煩惱重障，何況正
<lb ed="W" n="0421a14"/>心修念佛定。</p>
<lb ed="W" n="0421a15"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0421a16"/><juan fun="close" n="1"><jhead>佛說相好經<note n="0421010" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">本錄文尾題甲本作「佛相好經一卷」。</note><note n="0421011" resp="ZangWai" place="foot text" type="orig">底本卷尾有題記一則，為「清信佛弟子敦煌郡司法參軍馮如皂在住所自寫記之」。</note></jhead></juan>
<lb ed="W" n="0421a17"/>
<lb ed="W" n="0421a18"/><p id="pW03p0421a1801">〔錄文完〕</p></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>
